{"word":"ἦπου","slug":"ἦπου","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n47500\" key=\"h)=pou\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἦπου</orth> or <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἦ που</orth>, <sense id=\"n47500.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">I ween</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ που σοφὸς ἦν ὅστις ἔφασκεν . . </quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:725\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">725</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ που νέος γ᾽ ὢν ἦσθ᾽ ὑβριστής</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg008.perseus-grc1:63\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">63</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:43\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.43</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:830\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.830</biblScope> </bibl>; ironical, <pb n=\"777\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1008\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1008<